<i>noun</i>: 차출 [차출], 임용 [이ː묭], 임명 [임ː명], 약속 [약쏙], 보직 [보ː직], 발령 [발령], 등용 [등용], 기용 [기용] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt>차출 [차출]</dt><br>
<dd>assignment; appointment</dd><br>
<dd>어떤 일을 시키기 위하여 사람을 뽑음.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of assigning a certain task to someone.</dd><br>
<dt>임용 [이ː묭]</dt><br>
<dd>appointment; employment; hiring</dd><br>
<dd>직무를 맡기어 사람을 씀.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of hiring someone and assigning a certain job to him/her.</dd><br>
<dt>임명 [임ː명]</dt><br>
<dd>appointment; nomination; designation</dd><br>
<dd>어떤 사람에게 일정한 직위나 임무를 맡김.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of assigning a certain position or work to someone.</dd><br>
<dt>약속 [약쏙]</dt><br>
<dd>promise; appointment; pledge</dd><br>
<dd>다른 사람과 어떤 일을 하기로 미리 정함. 또는 그렇게 정한 내용.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of agreeing with someone to do a certain thing, or details of such an agreement.</dd><br>
<dt>보직 [보ː직]</dt><br>
<dd>appointment; assignment</dd><br>
<dd>어떤 직위와 함께 맡을 일을 줌. 또는 그 직위.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of assigning someone to a position and giving him/her work to do, or the assigned position.</dd><br>
<dt>발령 [발령]</dt><br>
<dd>1. appointment</dd><br>
<dd>직책이나 직위의 임명 또는 해임, 이동과 관련된 명령을 내림. 또는 그 명령.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of issuing directives with regard to the appointment, dismissal, or transfer of a person to or from a certain position or title ; or such a directive.</dd><br>
<dd>2. issuance</dd><br>
<dd>위험하거나 긴급한 상황에 대한 경보를 내림.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of issuing a warning against danger or emergency.</dd><br>
<dt>등용 [등용]</dt><br>
<dd>appointment</dd><br>
<dd>학식과 능력을 갖춘 사람을 뽑아 씀.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of appointing a person with ability and knowledge.</dd><br>
<dt>기용 [기용]</dt><br>
<dd>appointment</dd><br>
<dd>능력 있는 사람을 중요한 자리에 뽑아 씀.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of assigning a competent person to an important post.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>